  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Brexit operational readiness guidance for the health and care system in England
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Actions that providers and commissioners of health and social care services should take to prepare for, and manage, the risks of a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

